OL,3,C100 years on: How one of the world's
OL,4,Coldest buildings was found in Jersey
OL,6,FConstruction
OL,8,FThe tomb was built by our Neolithic
OL,9,Fancestors 6,000 years ago. It is
OL,10,Fthought it may have all started with a
OL,11,Fsingle standing stone, which would
OL,12,Fhave been a focus for the community to
OL,13,Fgather around. From there, they built
OL,14,Fa small open chamber with a cruciform
OL,15,Flayout.
OL,17,FNeolithic builders would then have
OL,18,Fcreated a passage and covered the
OL,19,Fentire monument with large capstones
OL,20,Fusing earth ramps, wooden rollers and
OL,21,Fa strong workforce.
