OL,3,C100 years on: How one of the world's
OL,4,Coldest buildings was found in Jersey
OL,6,FA friend of Dr Mourant, Debbie Millar,
OL,7,Fdescribes Arthur as someone who had a
OL,8,F"huge zest for life".
OL,10,FShe adds: "When the passage chamber
OL,11,Fwas finally discovered, Arthur wanted
OL,12,Feverybody to know about it so he
OL,13,Fjumped on his bicycle and he cycled
OL,14,Fround St Saviour saying, "We found it,
OL,15,Fwe've found it!".
OL,17,F"Whether anybody stopped to look I
OL,18,Fdon't know, but he was so excited and
OL,19,Fthat was typical of Arthur."
