OL,3,C100 years on: How one of the world's
OL,4,Coldest buildings was found in Jersey
OL,6,FA small quantity of human bones were
OL,7,Ffound scattered on the floor close to
OL,8,Fthe side chambers.
OL,10,FThey belonged to at least eight
OL,11,Fpeople, of whom two were definitely
OL,12,Ffemale and four male.
OL,14,FThe evidence could suggest that the
OL,15,Fbodies were exposed to the elements to
OL,16,Frot or had been buried elsewhere
OL,17,Fbefore being brought to their final
OL,18,Fresting place.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/13
