OL,3,C100 years on: How one of the world's
OL,4,Coldest buildings was found in Jersey
OL,6,FHowever, the small number of
OL,7,Findividuals represented does not
OL,8,Fnecessarily mean that burial was
OL,9,Freserved for just a privileged few.
OL,11,FIt is possible that many more people
OL,12,Fwere buried for a short time, in a
OL,13,Fsense 'just passing through' and that
OL,14,Fburial in the chamber was never
OL,15,Fintended to be permanent.
OL,17,FLimpet shells where found on top of
OL,18,Fsome of the capstones, believed to
OL,19,Fhave been placed there during the
OL,20,Fmound's construction.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/13
