OL,3,C100 years on: How one of the world's
OL,4,Coldest buildings was found in Jersey
OL,6,FThey may represent deliberate food
OL,7,Fofferings to provide nourishment in
OL,8,Fthe next world. The rituals and
OL,9,Fceremonies may have involved the
OL,10,Fsacrifice of animals for feasting as
OL,11,Fsome burnt bones was excavated.
OL,13,FThe burial of cattle in the interior
OL,14,Fsuggests a close identification of
OL,15,Fpeople with their herds.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/13
