OL,3,C100 years on: How one of the world's
OL,4,Coldest buildings was found in Jersey
OL,6,FTwo beads were found. In some
OL,7,Fsocieties, personal possessions are so
OL,8,Ffirmly associated with the deceased
OL,9,Fthat it is bad luck for someone else
OL,10,Fto own them so they are buried with
OL,11,Fthe owner.
OL,13,FThe items they were buried with are
OL,14,Fstrong evidence of a belief in the
OL,15,Fafterlife.
OL,17,FOlga Finch, Curator of Archaeology at
OL,18,FJersey Heritage, explains: "It is
OL,19,Freally a little insight into the
OL,20,Fhearts and the minds of our Neolithic
OL,21,Fancestors.
