OL,3,C100 years on: How one of the world's
OL,4,Coldest buildings was found in Jersey
OL,6,F"We know that this was a really
OL,7,Fspecial place, we know that they were
OL,8,Fburying the dead here because we have
OL,9,Ftheir remains such as personal
OL,10,Fornaments, food and tools for the
OL,11,Fafterlife. The dead were definitely
OL,12,Fcelebrated."
OL,14,FMore to learn
OL,16,FDespite significant digs in the early
OL,17,F1920s and 1990s, much of the site
OL,18,Fremains unexcavated and technological
OL,19,Fadvancements could help to uncover
OL,20,Fmore secrets.
